Comment=Switch EG character themes in Equestria OS
Comment[en]=Switch EG character themes in Equestria OS
Comment[ru]=Переключение тем персонажей EG в Equestria OS
Comment[de]=EG-Charakterthemen in EquestriaOS wechseln
Comment[fr]=Changer les thèmes de personnages EG dans Equestria OS
Comment[es]=Cambiar temas de personajes EG en Equestria OS
Comment[pt]=Alternar temas de personagens EG no Equestria OS
